        "prompt": "DO NOT USE TEMP DIRECTORIES. DO ALL WORK IN THIS DIRECTORY/SUBDIRECTORIES.\n\nFor each file across the subdirectories of ./test-agents, deploy an agent treating that file as an agents.md file. This agent will perform e2e testing on the codebase based on the behaviors prescribed in the .md file. Direct each agent to write results to its own uniquely identifiable output file in the subdirectory ./test_results/TEST_RESULTS_$1.{{turn}}\n\nDon't edit DESIGN_DOC.md, ARCHITECTURE.md, FEATURE_LIST_FULL.md, WAVE_BREAKDOWN.md, ./research, ./plans, ./test-agents, ./how-to-be-a-good-coder\n\nBased on the results in ./test_results/TEST_RESULTS_$1.{{turn}}, did ALL tests pass?",
